                <h3>Ceremony</h3>
                <p>The wedding ceremony is at <b>12:30 on 7th April 2018</b> at <b>Bisham Church, SL7 1RW</b></p>
                <p>Please note that there is only a portaloo at the church, so we recommend you use the toilets at the Bisham Abbey sports centre building (on your left as you enter the grounds) prior to the service.</p>
                <p>Parking: We have arranged for use of the co-located <b>Bisham School</b> car park for the ceremony. This should provide ample parking for all guests. The school and church are clearly signposted from the main road. Once you have turned off the main road, turn immediately right through the school gates. Continue round to the rear of the school for extended parking.</p>
                <p><b>Please relocate your car to Bisham Abbey for the reception, as the school gates will be locked after the ceremony.</b></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
                <img id="logo" class="featureImage" src="/img/circle_abbey.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Reception</h3>
                <p>The reception, following the ceremony is at <b>Bisham Abbey</b>, in the grounds of <b>Bisham Abbey National Sport Centre</b>.</p>
                <p>The entrance to Bisham Church and Bisham Abbey are at opposite ends of Bisham Village, on Bisham Road; about 900m apart.</p>
                <p>There will be a wedding breakfast at around 15:30. If you have any dietary requirements (such as vegetarian food), please include this on your RSVP.</p>
                <p>There will be light buffet and music and dancing in the evening.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
